Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.54,0:01:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚…來不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起住的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.43,0:01:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你提出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.11,0:01:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點興奮過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是要結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.43,0:02:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.61,0:02:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上要去醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快的話就趕不上探望時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.32,0:02:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.88,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是校前坡道上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很懷念吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就要超過你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.05,0:02:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可真篤定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  剛剛還是天晴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.73,0:03:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好像也很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.51,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石田小姐  真快呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是去拿些文件而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花不了多少時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在複印什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過這個不用複印嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？說過？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近你常出差錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰到什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.73,0:04:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我聊聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒也沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點心不在焉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海鮮炒飯和日式漢堡套餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請快一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.62,0:04:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  羽澤商貿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  請稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫鳴海的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都打到公司來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.74,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的問題不小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心別被別人看出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝成是客戶打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思在你上班的時候打給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為打你手機打不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.80,0:05:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天下班後有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見了面再具體說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼六點柊町見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.98,0:05:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.74,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩被我們逮個正著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮  真由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們什麼時候來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說『啊，是我』的那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就盯上你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用店裏的電話都幹了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.11,0:06:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.49,0:06:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大空寺用店裏的電話辦私事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.76,0:06:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個的確有點不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.87,0:06:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打私人電話的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用了說一聲就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想混過去的話就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和玉野去大堂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你打的是市內電話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去踩貓屎吧！！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  突然之間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這一帶開始看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的工資加起來大概這一帶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是朝南的好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是太貴了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  那我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這不是壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是說想忘了遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在的我們有自己的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.06,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…和你的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的不太滿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.77,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.22,0:08:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯  恭喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是預選賽  還不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的自信還有實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不累嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不偶爾放鬆一下會撐不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞎操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…也不算啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了  定期檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想立刻就進行恢復性治療
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那也得等她醒了再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香月醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市丸和長田又把酒帶進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說過多少遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次還把烏龜帶進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.90,0:10:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏龜？想要放在哪里養啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有重大事情報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.40,0:10:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本人今天在地區預選賽中奪魁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是壓倒性的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.58,0:10:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.77,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香月醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後再來造訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.20,0:11:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.94,0:11:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有決定？ 房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總找不到好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會不會找到房子前就分手了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有空嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到一家店裏的葡萄酒不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.25,0:12:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死心塌地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來…吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的咖喱大概有點偏辣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.19,0:12:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始你用『章魚』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦一熱就變得通紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.58,0:12:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.83,0:12:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼暫時把『海豚』借給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 飯要涼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.83,0:12:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好辣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說過的吧  夏天還是辣點的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.78,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是店裏打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接了就要多幹活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是鳴海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事的話請在聽到提示音後留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這實在是太辣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聲電話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是大空寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我把夜班推給她所以來發火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是涼宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.69,0:13:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事必須讓你知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才打電話過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.94,0:13:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該早點跟你說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.47,0:13:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她醒過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.16,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽要睡這裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人很可憐吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.24,0:14:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我給鳴海家裏打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.63,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在不去看遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之  你會後悔一輩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.05,0:15:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.25,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想你再變回那時候的孝之了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.82,0:16:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.32,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香月大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫速瀨吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把頭髮剪了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.14,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.73,0:16:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海君現在在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一家餐廳打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是放棄考試了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她醒來快一個月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體恢復得非常順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖然能讓你們和她見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是必須遵守一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.18,0:17:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間的間隔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那以來已經過了3年這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還停留在那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停留在那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮  鳴海君來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.85,0:17:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？孝之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.72,0:18:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.46,0:18:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該道歉的那個是我才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家這麼擔心 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了  孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞到我都想哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月  你也來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康復了就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.02,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  連環畫展已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道以後還會在別的地方開嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.11,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 第二學期開始就要忙於復習迎考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.07,0:19:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得可以和孝之一起去看的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.43,0:19:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定還會再開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時再和哥哥一起去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.99,0:19:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要總是學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要放鬆放鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呀  遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像茜說的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點好起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也做不了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.98,0:20:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 水月也來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.57,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.87,0:20:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮  讓我量下體溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.09,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是太累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微躺著休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把床放下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 慢慢的 慢慢的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.92,0:20:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.07,0:20:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和這個人一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把她帶到姐姐那裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.85,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.93,0:21:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來向姐姐炫耀你們感情融洽嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然還有臉站在姐姐面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.02,0:21:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好恩愛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧在三年來讓姐姐孤零零一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.17,0:21:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己卻快樂地享受著戀愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜  聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫得那麼親熱
